# Deny everything; allow only tracked config. Each config/ subdir owns its
# own allowlist in this format (deny all, then re-include specifics).
# See config/.gitignore.

*
!.gitignore
!000-loadtokens
!010-general
!aider
!ansible
!app_env_vars
!bash_prompt
!binenv
!calibre
!claude
!cuda
!docker
!gh
!git
!go
!grok
!less
!nodejs
!perl
!python
!rust
!.shellcheckrc
!ssh-config-completion
!taskwarrior_inactive
!terraform
!tmux
!vim
!zzz-check-dotfiles
!zzz-check-dotvim
